OL,4,CFrome couple lose savings in Royal Mail
OL,5,Ctext scam
OL,6, A couple have been left "heartbroken"
OL,7, after being tricked out of their
OL,8, savings in a Royal Mail text scam.
OL,10,FTom and Freyja Cuff, from Frome,
OL,11,FSomerset, received a text about a
OL,12,Fparcel collection which eventually led
OL,13,Fto their bank account being emptied of
OL,14,F#2,500.
OL,16,FA spokesperson for Trading Standards
OL,17,Fsaid this sort of scam was very common
OL,18,Fand that "Covid was a scammers dream".
OL,20,FMr Cuff said: "We were left with
OL,21,Fabsolutely nothing."
